# Repository Structure

```
qwen-agent-runtime/
  agent/
    __main__.py      # Entry point, chat loop
    core.py           # LLM initialization
    guardrails.py     # Safety checks
    executor.py       # Command execution
  config/
    config.yaml       # LLM keys, agent ID, shell
  scripts/
    bootstrap_awesome_ps.ps1  # Module installer
  presentation/
    main.qd           # This presentation
  README.md
```

Python 3.10+ required. OpenAI SDK for LLM communication.

