# Get Started

```bash
# Clone
git clone https://codeberg.org/cubiczan/qwen-agent-runtime.git
cd qwen-agent-runtime

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Configure your LLM key and agent ID
notepad config/config.yaml

# Run
python -m agent
```

> Important: The agent runs locally. Commands execute locally. Your API keys stay on your machine.

